Medical and Agricultural Disclaimer

This software is developed strictly for academic research and educational
purposes. The predictions generated by this system are based on a machine
learning model trained on controlled laboratory images from the PlantVillage
dataset. They do not constitute professional agronomic or phytopathological
advice. Do not use this system as the sole basis for crop management, pesticide
application, or any other agricultural decision without independent validation
by a qualified plant pathologist or agronomist.

